faq-row"><div class="col-sm-6" id="about-the-protector-layla-essential-mattress-protector"><h5>About The Protector</h5><div class="sep-faq" id="accor_613783"><div class="toggtitle">1. Do I need a mattress protector?<i class="fa fa-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><div class="toggcontent"><p>If you had any idea of all the nasty that can grow inside your mattress by not having a protector, you wouldn’t be asking that question. We wouldn’t sleep on a mattress for a single night without a protector and we don’t think you should either. In fact mattress protectors are so important that not having one can void your mattress warranty.</p></div></div><div class="sep-faq" id="accor_613785"><div class="toggtitle">2. What does the mattress protector help protect against?<i class="fa fa-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><div class="toggcontent"><p>The Layla® Mattress Protectors help protect you from your mattress and your mattress from you. The Essential and Cooling protectors help protect against stains, pet or human bodily fluids, dead skin cells, and dust mites. The Encasement protector will also prevent bed bug entry and escape. All protectors are hypoallergenic and breathable.</p></div></div><div class="sep-faq" id="accor_613786"><div class="toggtitle">3. Is the mattress protector liquid proof?<i class="fa fa-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><div class="toggcontent"><p>The Essential, Cooling, and Encasement protectors are liquid proof and have been tested up to 38 pounds per square inch of water pressure so your mattress can handle whatever life throws at it.</p></div></div><div class="sep-faq" id="accor_613788"><div class="toggtitle">4. Will the mattress protector fit my mattress?<i class="fa fa-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><div class="toggcontent"><p>Although our mattress protectors are designed to perfectly fit the Layla® Mattress and Layla Hybrid™, Layla® Mattress Protectors will fit any mattress up to 14” deep.</p></div></div><div class="sep-faq" id="accor_613790"><div class="toggtitle">5. Is the protector noisy?<i class="fa fa-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><div class="toggcontent"><p>Nope. We cringe at those other protectors that sound like a vinyl record being scratched everytime you move around in bed. Layla® Mattress protectors are made with high quality silent materials so you’ll never even know it’s there.</p></div></div><div class="sep-faq" id="accor_613787"><div class="toggtitle">6. Will the mattress protector make me sleep hot?<i class="fa fa-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><div class="toggcontent"><p>Layla® Mattress protectors are made breathable to help prevent you from sleeping hot. The Cooling Protector is made with fibers that are cold to the touch for a cool comfortable sleep all night long.</p></div></div><div class="sep-faq" id="accor_613791"><div class="toggtitle">7. Which protector is right for me?<i class="fa fa-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><div class="toggcontent"><p>It depends. All three protectors will protect against allergens, dust mites, dead skin cells and bodily fluids that can turn into fungus or mold. If you’re looking for 5 sided protection without breaking the bank the Essential is right for you. For hot sleepers that want all the benefits of the Essential with added cooling then The Cooling Protector is what you need. And if you need protection against bed bugs then you’ll need The Full Encasement Protector with PESTLOC zipper.</p></div></div><div class="sep-faq" id="accor_613792"><div class="toggtitle">8. Will having a mattress protector increase the lifespan of my mattress?<i class="fa fa-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><div class="toggcontent"><p>On average having a mattress with a mattress protector used daily can last up to 3 times longer than a mattress without protection.</p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6" id="shipping-layla-essential-mattress-protector-layla-essential-mattress-protector"><h5>Shipping</h5><div class="sep-faq" id="accor_703160"><div class